bioghist.p: This assembled collection consists of diplomas issued to University of Michigan students from various departments and colleges. Also included is a sample of a corrected blank form to be used in 1845 if engraved diplomas did not arrive in time.

scopecontent.p: The Diplomas collection consists of approximately 150 diplomas issued by the University of Michigan, 1845-1934, as well as some special program diplomas and certificates and seven diplomas for other institutions of higher education.
